WEBVTT

00:00:00.486 --> 00:00:02.312
Track 02.07

00:00:03.869 --> 00:00:05.198
Speaker 1

00:00:06.306 --> 00:00:07.393
Darren: I’m Darren.

00:00:07.456 --> 00:00:10.472
I’m the manager of a TV shop in Manchester.

00:00:11.092 --> 00:00:12.597
I don’t have an office,

00:00:12.622 --> 00:00:13.911
but I have a chair

00:00:14.027 --> 00:00:15.401
and a desk in the shop.

00:00:16.040 --> 00:00:18.940
It’s an old desk and it isn't big,

00:00:19.016 --> 00:00:21.340
but I have a phone, a computer

00:00:21.555 --> 00:00:23.751
and a newspaper on my desk,

00:00:24.121 --> 00:00:26.131
and the keys to the shop.

00:00:27.302 --> 00:00:29.007
Speaker 2

00:00:29.612 --> 00:00:30.961
Paula: I’m Paula.

00:00:31.279 --> 00:00:33.342
I’m a teacher in Washington.

00:00:33.660 --> 00:00:35.684
I have three desks!

00:00:35.961 --> 00:00:37.211
One at home,

00:00:37.430 --> 00:00:39.652
one in the teachers’ room at the school,

00:00:39.910 --> 00:00:41.755
and one in my classroom.

00:00:42.282 --> 00:00:43.988
I have a laptop and some

00:00:44.018 --> 00:00:46.196
books on my desk in the teachers’ room

00:00:46.433 --> 00:00:48.326
but I don’t have a phone.

00:00:48.757 --> 00:00:51.818
Today, my bag is on my desk

00:00:51.991 --> 00:00:53.769
with my umbrella.

00:00:54.405 --> 00:00:56.389
Speaker 3

00:00:56.587 --> 00:00:58.134
Jamie: I’m Jamie.

00:00:58.373 --> 00:01:00.992
I’m a student in Southampton.

00:01:01.309 --> 00:01:03.472
I have a desk at school

00:01:03.690 --> 00:01:05.744
and another desk in my bedroom

00:01:05.769 --> 00:01:07.270
where I do my homework.

00:01:08.025 --> 00:01:10.605
I have a computer on my desk at home,

00:01:10.671 --> 00:01:13.600
and today I also have an apple

00:01:13.796 --> 00:01:16.495
and a knife and a glass of water.